<i>Severa has passed away</i>

1:24:42.525 --> 1:24:45.845
<i>Severa has passed away</i>

1:24:46.565 --> 1:24:50.205
<i>Severa has passed away</i>

1:24:51.085 --> 1:24:54.685
<i>And the streets of Mouraria</i>

1:24:55.245 --> 1:24:59.445
<i>Weep with anger and pain</i>

1:24:59.965 --> 1:25:03.245
<i>And the streets of Mouraria</i>

1:25:03.845 --> 1:25:07.925
<i>Weep with anger and pain</i>

1:25:08.285 --> 1:25:11.685
<i>A black shawl, a black shawl</i>

1:25:12.205 --> 1:25:15.885
