1:25:17.085 --> 1:25:20.765
<i>A black shawl, a black shawl</i>

1:25:21.405 --> 1:25:24.925
<i>Black like the new moon</i>

1:25:25.685 --> 1:25:29.245
<i>As black as the darkest night</i>

1:25:29.605 --> 1:25:32.245
<i>As black as the darkest night</i>

1:26:01.405 --> 1:26:04.845
You two are under arrest
in the name of the Portuguese government.

1:26:05.805 --> 1:26:06.925
No.

1:26:07.845 --> 1:26:09.325
She hasn't done anything!

1:26:11.645 --> 1:26:13.125
She hasn't done anything!

1:26:19.525 --> 1:26:20.845
Be careful, she's...

1:26:20.925 --> 1:26:22.485
Shut up and keep moving!

1:27:23.685 --> 1:27:24.765
Come on, walk!

1:27:28.565 --> 1:27:33.925
Here I have a lawsuit
from the Court of A Coruña...

1:27:35.085 --> 1:27:39.325
which says that you are
a woman called Elisa,

1:27:40.445 --> 1:27:43.605
and that, with a false identity,

1:27:43.685 --> 1:27:47.165
you managed to get married to Marcela...

1:27:48.365 --> 1:27:49.485
and entered Portugal.

1:27:51.445 --> 1:27:52.325
I'm Mario.

1:27:54.725 --> 1:27:56.445
Please, I don't have all day.

1:27:57.965 --> 1:28:02.765
What is this comedy that you
and this woman have concocted?

1:28:03.165 --> 1:28:05.085
That woman is my wife.

1:28:06.365 --> 1:28:11.605
You Spaniards are always so stubborn,
so pig-headed, so loud-mouthed.

1:28:18.165 --> 1:28:20.765
Please, sir, she... my wife...

1:28:21.885 --> 1:28:23.805
has nothing to do with all this.

1:28:24.485 --> 1:28:25.565
She knows nothing.

1:28:26.085 --> 1:28:28.765
She thinks that I'm a hermaphrodite,
that I...

1:28:30.285 --> 1:28:31.725
Please, stop,

1:28:31.805 --> 1:28:34.765
Elisa, Mario, whatever your name is.

1:28:35.365 --> 1:28:38.885
I'm not an ignorant parish priest
from a village in Galicia

1:28:38.965 --> 1:28:42.165
who you and your friend
can fool that easily.

1:28:46.885 --> 1:28:49.445
If I tell the guards right now...

1:28:50.005 --> 1:28:52.405
to take you to the men's prison cell,

1:28:53.245 --> 1:28:56.485
how long do you think it will take them
to find out what you are?

1:28:57.765 --> 1:28:58.765
How long?

