Not long...

1:29:08.565 --> 1:29:09.525
I guess.

1:29:28.365 --> 1:29:29.765
Are you pregnant?

1:29:32.045 --> 1:29:32.965
Yes?

1:29:33.605 --> 1:29:34.645
Come.

1:29:35.165 --> 1:29:36.125
Come here.

1:29:44.085 --> 1:29:45.005
Eat.

1:30:10.845 --> 1:30:12.405
What will happen to us?

1:30:16.685 --> 1:30:18.045
What are we accused of?

1:30:19.285 --> 1:30:20.645
Transvestism.

1:30:23.205 --> 1:30:24.325
Blasphemy.

1:30:27.525 --> 1:30:29.525
Falsifying documents.

1:30:30.805 --> 1:30:33.365
And your friend is accused
of being an accomplice.

1:30:33.725 --> 1:30:36.005
That's just across the border.

1:30:36.605 --> 1:30:39.445
But first, you have to answer
the charges on this side.

1:30:40.005 --> 1:30:41.405
You'll be tried here,

1:30:41.605 --> 1:30:45.325
and then transferred to Galicia.

1:30:48.685 --> 1:30:51.925
It's all my fault.
Marcela is innocent, I swear.

1:30:56.565 --> 1:30:58.205
She's expecting a child.

1:31:01.565 --> 1:31:02.605
A child?

1:31:09.965 --> 1:31:11.405
Put a dress on.

1:31:11.565 --> 1:31:14.165
I'll tell them to put you
in the women's building.

1:31:24.325 --> 1:31:25.565
Can I be with her?

1:31:26.125 --> 1:31:27.005
Yes.

1:31:30.885 --> 1:31:31.805
Thank you.

1:31:34.685 --> 1:31:36.205
You're a good person.

1:31:36.725 --> 1:31:37.725
You're welcome.

1:31:37.805 --> 1:31:40.925
That's what my wife says
when she's about to upset me.

1:31:42.325 --> 1:31:43.605
Go, go, go.

1:31:44.365 --> 1:31:45.325
Leave.

1:31:45.405 --> 1:31:47.405
Before I regret it

1:31:47.485 --> 1:31:49.565
and lock you up with those savages.

1:31:59.085 --> 1:31:59.965
Go on.

1:32:19.605 --> 1:32:20.685
Marcela.

1:32:26.645 --> 1:32:27.605
Mario.

1:32:29.485 --> 1:32:30.565
I'm Elisa.

1:32:35.845 --> 1:32:36.805
Elisa.

1:33:12.165 --> 1:33:13.765
What's going to happen now?

1:33:25.965 --> 1:33:26.965
I don't know.

1:33:44.125 --> 1:33:45.725
But we're together.

1:33:50.045 --> 1:33:51.205
Together, yes.

1:34:02.005 --> 1:34:03.165
Forgive me.

1:34:10.565 --> 1:34:12.325
I said I would protect you...

1:34:13.685 --> 1:34:16.005
-and look where we are.
-No, Elisa, shh.

1:34:18.445 --> 1:34:20.125
You don't have to apologize.

1:34:27.565 --> 1:34:28.885
We'll get out of here.

1:34:34.285 --> 1:34:36.645
We should have left a long time ago.

1:34:44.085 --> 1:34:45.165
Maybe.

1:34:51.645 --> 1:34:53.925
I'm scared that our baby
will be born here.

1:35:03.005 --> 1:35:04.645
The warden will help us.

1:35:06.605 --> 1:35:08.165
He seems to be a good man.

1:35:12.445 --> 1:35:14.725
We need more than just a good man.

1:35:38.165 --> 1:35:39.085
Keep still.

1:35:43.565 --> 1:35:44.485
Perfect.

1:35:45.365 --> 1:35:46.325
Ready?

1:36:03.245 --> 1:36:06.325
Have you read about
those two women that got married?

1:36:07.245 --> 1:36:12.445
If we send them back to Spain, they'll be
sentenced to prison for 20 years.

1:36:21.205 --> 1:36:24.125
It was made with great affection.
Please give this to them.

1:36:24.205 --> 1:36:25.805
Of course, I'll deliver it to them.

1:36:25.885 --> 1:36:28.365
I have a gift for the child
of the Spanish women.

1:36:28.445 --> 1:36:30.285
Please give them this.

1:36:35.605 --> 1:36:36.805
It brings good luck.

1:36:41.885 --> 1:36:44.845
That's enough touching.
Let's have some order here.

1:36:48.765 --> 1:36:49.645
Elisa...

1:36:56.685 --> 1:36:57.605
It's coming!

1:37:01.005 --> 1:37:02.085
Are you sure?

1:37:02.805 --> 1:37:03.725
Yes.

1:37:09.245 --> 1:37:11.365
There's the head. It's coming!

1:37:11.445 --> 1:37:13.245
Breathe.

1:37:13.405 --> 1:37:16.285
Look, here it comes! Go, push.

1:37:17.645 --> 1:37:20.245
Push hard! Come on!

1:37:21.885 --> 1:37:24.965
Now, this is it. One last time!

1:37:51.685 --> 1:37:53.005
So much hair!

1:37:53.085 --> 1:37:53.925
Right?

1:37:54.965 --> 1:37:56.685
Hello.

1:38:13.845 --> 1:38:15.525
Oh, nice and healthy.

1:38:16.205 --> 1:38:17.805
A girl. It's a girl.

1:38:17.885 --> 1:38:19.245
What's her name?

1:38:19.525 --> 1:38:21.325
-Ana.
-Oh, she's beautiful.

1:38:21.445 --> 1:38:24.325
GOVERNOR'S PALACE, PORTO

1:38:25.045 --> 1:38:28.805
Commissioner, what's this story about
the two Spanish women that got married?

1:38:28.885 --> 1:38:32.245
My wife won't stop going on about it.

1:38:34.085 --> 1:38:36.405
She even wants to visit them in prison.

1:38:37.765 --> 1:38:39.485
They've had a lot of visitors,

1:38:39.565 --> 1:38:40.525
that is true.

1:38:42.125 --> 1:38:44.605
The Spanish authorities are pressuring me.

1:38:45.565 --> 1:38:47.485
They want to try them in A Coruña.

1:38:47.845 --> 1:38:50.445
I think they want to make
an example of them both.

1:38:51.685 --> 1:38:54.885
They're not criminals,
they're two women who are--

1:38:54.965 --> 1:38:55.885
Stupid.

1:38:59.085 --> 1:39:00.725
This cod is so bland.

1:39:04.645 --> 1:39:06.085
What's the current situation?

1:39:07.445 --> 1:39:09.645
One of them gave birth
to a baby girl in prison.

1:39:10.045 --> 1:39:11.285
Gave birth in prison?

1:39:12.325 --> 1:39:13.565
Just what we needed.

1:39:16.005 --> 1:39:16.885
Governor...

1:39:17.485 --> 1:39:20.085
If we hand them over
to the Spanish authorities,

1:39:20.165 --> 1:39:22.005
they'll get ten to 20 years in jail.

1:39:29.165 --> 1:39:33.605
Can I count on your esteemed help
so that doesn't happen?

1:39:34.365 --> 1:39:35.965
Done legally, of course.

1:39:36.965 --> 1:39:39.565
Even if it's just to annoy the Spanish.

1:39:42.325 --> 1:39:44.725
Your Excellency, count on me.

1:39:48.765 --> 1:39:50.805
Try this cod
and tell me if it isn't bland.

1:39:50.885 --> 1:39:52.005
No, thank you, Governor.

1:40:08.205 --> 1:40:10.525
We have enough for both fares, Marcela.

1:40:11.605 --> 1:40:13.525
As soon as we get out of here...

1:40:14.685 --> 1:40:17.325
If we leave here,
they'll hand us over to the authorities.

1:40:24.605 --> 1:40:26.205
Something's wrong with her.

1:40:26.365 --> 1:40:27.285
It's the humidity...

1:40:28.845 --> 1:40:29.845
and this place.

1:40:37.605 --> 1:40:38.605
Give her to me.

1:40:38.685 --> 1:40:39.565
No.

1:40:42.005 --> 1:40:43.005
What's wrong?

1:40:46.325 --> 1:40:48.525
Come here.

1:40:55.045 --> 1:40:56.085
She's burning up.

1:41:02.005 --> 1:41:03.085
A doctor!

1:41:03.605 --> 1:41:05.405
We need a doctor!

1:41:06.565 --> 1:41:08.165
It's the baby! A doctor!

1:41:22.565 --> 1:41:23.765
Shh, calm down.

1:41:35.765 --> 1:41:36.765
Listen...

1:41:38.525 --> 1:41:39.925
The baby has pneumonia.

1:41:40.365 --> 1:41:42.765
We have to lower her fever or she'll die.

1:41:42.845 --> 1:41:44.805
They can come with me to my house.

1:41:46.885 --> 1:41:48.125
Let's go to my house.

1:42:29.445 --> 1:42:30.445
Get some sleep.

1:42:43.205 --> 1:42:45.165
-Well?
-How are they?

1:42:45.685 --> 1:42:47.005
I think she's out of danger.

1:42:48.685 --> 1:42:49.965
Now they're sleeping.

1:42:54.285 --> 1:42:55.885
The baby is very beautiful.

1:42:57.405 --> 1:43:00.045
I can't thank you enough
for everything you've done for us.

1:43:01.525 --> 1:43:03.045
It's a privilege to have met you.

1:43:05.445 --> 1:43:07.085
Most people wouldn't say that.

1:43:08.605 --> 1:43:10.525
We're not most people.

1:43:11.285 --> 1:43:12.125
Right?

1:43:15.165 --> 1:43:16.045
Right.

1:43:19.485 --> 1:43:20.885
You don't have children?

1:43:21.365 --> 1:43:22.205
No.

1:43:47.885 --> 1:43:50.645
I can't detain you two any longer, Elisa.

1:43:52.245 --> 1:43:54.645
But if I let you go, you'll be deported.

1:43:54.725 --> 1:43:55.645
I know.

1:44:08.565 --> 1:44:10.285
If I were to let you go...

1:44:10.925 --> 1:44:12.365
This is only an example.

1:44:13.205 --> 1:44:15.805
...the day before the boat leaves.

1:44:16.125 --> 1:44:19.525
And on the release papers,
I put a date of, let's say...

1:44:20.485 --> 1:44:22.325
two days later.

1:44:27.005 --> 1:44:29.565
But first we have to let them recover.

1:44:30.285 --> 1:44:31.165
Yes.

1:44:35.045 --> 1:44:37.365
Oh, you earn more.

1:44:37.445 --> 1:44:39.045
More money coming in.

1:44:39.845 --> 1:44:41.405
The others don't matter.

1:44:43.045 --> 1:44:45.405
We have to find a way to resolve things.

1:44:55.365 --> 1:44:56.325
Where's Ana?

1:45:02.565 --> 1:45:03.525
She's with Flor.

1:45:06.845 --> 1:45:09.765
I asked her to take care of her
until we're ready.

1:45:20.525 --> 1:45:21.845
Marcela, are you okay?

1:45:22.645 --> 1:45:24.005
Is something wrong?

1:45:29.885 --> 1:45:31.885
I thought you'd be happy
that we're leaving.

1:45:32.365 --> 1:45:33.325
I am.

1:45:34.365 --> 1:45:35.285
Believe me.

1:45:40.245 --> 1:45:41.365
You don't seem it.

1:45:49.765 --> 1:45:51.965
Soon we'll be out of this prison.

1:45:56.245 --> 1:45:57.445
This prison is fine.

1:46:02.165 --> 1:46:03.845
The problem is what's outside.

1:46:06.445 --> 1:46:08.245
Where we are carnival freaks.

1:46:12.165 --> 1:46:13.725
Where people stare at us.

1:46:14.645 --> 1:46:16.005
Where they laugh at us.

1:46:20.845 --> 1:46:22.285
Where there's no escape.

1:46:25.125 --> 1:46:26.565
And there never will be.

1:46:32.005 --> 1:46:34.205
That's why we got married
and came up with Mario.

1:46:34.285 --> 1:46:35.885
That's why I had my daughter.

1:46:40.045 --> 1:46:42.005
I thought they'd believe us then.

1:46:47.685 --> 1:46:49.445
How could I do this to my daughter?

1:46:52.925 --> 1:46:54.045
How could I?

1:47:02.645 --> 1:47:04.005
-My love...
-Elisa.

1:47:27.445 --> 1:47:28.405
Listen to me.

1:47:33.805 --> 1:47:36.325
Despite the fact
that I love you more than my own life,

1:47:40.085 --> 1:47:42.925
if you choose to stay here
with your daughter, I'll understand.

1:47:44.165 --> 1:47:46.725
I'll wait for you forever, Marcela.
Forever.

1:47:56.725 --> 1:47:58.285
Don't you understand?

1:48:03.405 --> 1:48:06.445
She's the one I'm leaving behind. Her.

1:48:27.285 --> 1:48:28.205
Thank you.

1:48:35.445 --> 1:48:38.925
Elisa, tell her that we'll tell the child
who her mother is.

1:48:39.885 --> 1:48:41.085
Yes, I'll tell her.

1:48:44.565 --> 1:48:45.565
Look after her...

1:48:46.485 --> 1:48:47.925
and look after yourself.

1:50:28.245 --> 1:50:30.285
I hated you, you know?

1:50:34.925 --> 1:50:36.565
For many years.

1:50:39.245 --> 1:50:42.085
-I can imagine.
-But they were very good parents.

1:50:43.325 --> 1:50:44.485
The best.

1:50:50.325 --> 1:50:51.565
I knew they would be.

1:51:00.085 --> 1:51:01.365
Was it worth it?

1:51:03.965 --> 1:51:04.965
All this?

1:51:07.045 --> 1:51:09.285
The wedding, the mockery?

1:51:11.045 --> 1:51:12.085
Going to prison?

1:51:14.485 --> 1:51:15.725
Abandoning me?

1:51:19.485 --> 1:51:20.805
Was it worth it?

